	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you've modified a NES to have sound, make sure you put the right resistor. I got the exact same problem with Just Breed the first time I tried expansion sound, because I've put a 100 Ohm resistor instead of 100 kiloohm. This just make the sound a lot louder.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
